<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1122304-why-does-waley-s-title-refer-to-sei">Why does Waley&#39;s title refer to Sei Shonagon as a courtesan?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1122304'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F18185.The_Pillow_Book">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1122304-why-does-waley-s-title-refer-to-sei">4 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1122304-why-does-waley-s-title-refer-to-sei">Add your answer</a>
</li>
