<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/20738920-orinoco-womble-tidy-bag-and-all"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1406361683i/20738920._UX100_CR0,18,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/20738920-orinoco-womble-tidy-bag-and-all">Orinoco Womble (tidy bag and all)</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Because Waley tended to see things in the court of Kyoto as he chose to see them. She was a lady-in-waiting at the court, but not a &quot;courtesan&quot;--and w<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">‚Ä¶more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Because Waley tended to see things in the court of Kyoto as he chose to see them. She was a lady-in-waiting at the court, but not a "courtesan"--and well he knew it. Shonagon was many things but she was not a "courtesan."<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
